<h1 class='doclevel'>1.Test Suite : lair3551_BBT</h1>
<div><p>Se testează adăugarea unui produs.</p>
</div><a name="toc_tc28072"></a><p>&nbsp;</p><div> <table class="tc" width="90%" ><tr><th colspan="4">Test Case P233-14: AdaugareProdusTestcase-ECP&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 80%;">[Version  : 1]</span></th></tr>
