<tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Summary:</span><br /><p>Se adaugă un produs folosind date valide.</p>
</td></tr><tr><td colspan="4"><span class="label">Preconditions:</span><br /><p>id: int, id &gt;=0</p>

<p>name: string , len(nume) &gt; 0, len(nume) &lt;= 255</p>

<p>price: double, pret &gt; 0, pret &lt;= 10000</p>

<p>category: DrinkCategory, să existe &icirc;n sistem</p>

<p>drinkbase: DrinkBase, să existe &icirc;n sistem&nbsp;</p>
</td></tr><tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Execution type:</span></td><td colspan="3">Automated</td></tr>
