<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Importance:</span></td><td colspan="3">Medium</td></tr>
<tr><td colspan="4"></td></tr><tr><td > name of the autotest class:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.ProductTest</td></tr>
<tr><td > name of the test method:</td><td  colspan = "3" >drinkshop.service.ProductTest#testAddValidProductECP</td></tr>
<tr><td width="20%" valign="top"><span class="label">Requirements</span><td colspan="3">lair3551_F01:  AdaugareProduse [Version : 1]<br /></td></tr>
